author: cmpilato
msg: Make the RA loader sanity-check the revisions passed through the revprop-
related interfaces so the various implementations don't have to.
Note: The underlying RA layers basically require valid revisions
anyway -- if not by explicitly checking themselves, then at least by
falling on their faces when handed something invalid.  And the API
never explicitly permitted invalid revisions.  So, I'm not feeling too
Assert that we were given a valid revision.
